<headline>Special Weather Statement issued December 31 at 10:03PM EST  by NWS Boston</headline>
<description>...PATCHY DENSE FOG THIS EVENING...
Areas of patchy dense fog likely tonight across southern New
England. Dense fog is more likely along the south coast, Cape,
and Islands where a dense fog advisory remains in effect.
Motorists can expect to encounter sudden changes in visibility.
Travel at reduced speeds and use low beam headlights in foggy
areas.</description>
